column2: SELECT rg.MPA_IDX, rg.RA, rg.DEC, rg.Z, rg.objid as id, n.objid, n.distance, p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r, s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, s.z as sz, pz.z as photoz, pz.zErr, pz.photoErrorClass as Class, pz.absMagu, pz.absMagg, pz.absMagr, pz.absMagi, pz.absMagz, sm.mstellar_median, abs (rg.Z-pz.z) as zdif INTO #tt FROM MyDB.RgalTot AS rg OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (rg.RA, rg.DEC, rg.R) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid = p.objid LEFT JOIN SpecObj as s ON n.objid = s.bestobjid LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid = pz.objid LEFT JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# as sm ON s.specobjid = sm.specobjid WHERE pz.z > #. GO SELECT tt.* FROM #tt as tt WHERE tt.zdif< # and #< tt.Class and tt.Class< # ORDER BY tt.MPA_IDX INTO MyDB.AGNsyVecPhoto
